msgstr ""

#: ../../source/data_integrity.rst:87 f4ab5f24ec484f4187c2b5748af7ff0d
msgid ""
"Are there sources that indicate the 1 Battalion moved in between these two "
"points of time and thus these should be treated as separate deployments to "
